      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 234.23333333333332
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_05-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、おかげで沖縄が大好きになっちゃった\nまたみんなで沖縄に来たいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ thanks to you‚ I really like the place now.\nI hope we all come here again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 234.23333333333332,
      "endTime": 242.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 242.76666666666668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_05-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "……優ちゃん、いろいろ助けてくれてありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu-chan‚ thanks for all your help.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 242.76666666666668,
      "endTime": 246.67331058184308,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 246.86666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_05-hrk017.m4a",
      "text": "私は地味で華もなくて大事な所でいつも運が悪くて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m plain with no glamor‚ and I always have bad luck when it really matters‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 246.86666666666667,
      "endTime": 253.1174151102702,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_05-hrk018.m4a",
      "text": "こんな私がサニピにふさわしいのかなって\n思ったこともあったけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so I’ve even wondered whether someone like me\nreally belongs in Sunny Peace…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 253.33333333333334,
      "endTime": 259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 257.03333333333336
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 259.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_05-hrk019.m4a",
      "text": "今回の旅で、みんなが私を必要としてくれていると\n分かって嬉しかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "On this trip I realized that everyone needs me‚\nand that makes me happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 259.2,
      "endTime": 264.8399503628413,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 265.03333333333336
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_05-hrk020.m4a",
      "text": "今なら胸を張って、私はサニピの一員だって言えるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now I can say with pride that I’m a member of Sunny Peace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 265.03333333333336,
      "endTime": 269.83088429768884,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 270.03333333333336
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_05-yu017.m4a",
      "text": "……遙子さんはもっと自信持ってええと思うわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I reckon you should have a whole lot more confidence in yerself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 270.03333333333336,
      "endTime": 273.7397051652273,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 273.93333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_05-yu018.m4a",
      "text": "目の前にまぶしいほどの才能の塊がおって\nそれに比べて自分は地味で凡人やと思ってて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y'all got all these talented prodigies in front of ya‚\nso ya feel plain and ordinary in comparison.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 273.93333333333334,
      "endTime": 281.76666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_05-yu019.m4a",
      "text": "せやけど腐らずに一生懸命努力して\nみんなからグループに不可欠な存在やと認められて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But y'all work hard and do yer best‚\nand everyone recognizes that y'all are an essential presence in the group.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 281.96666666666664,
      "endTime": 289.76666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 289.96666666666664
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_05-yu020.m4a",
      "text": "そんなひたむきで頑張り屋な遙子さんのこと\nうちは尊敬してるんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That earnest and hard-workin' Haruko-san is\nsomeone I deeply respect.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 289.96666666666664,
      "endTime": 295.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 295.6333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_05-hrk021.m4a",
      "text": "……ありがとう、優ちゃん\nこれからもお互い頑張ろうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks‚ Yu-chan.\nLet’s both do our best from now on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 295.6333333333333,
      "endTime": 301.26666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 298.93333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_05-yu021.m4a",
      "text": "……せやね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes‚ let's do that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 301.46666666666664,
      "endTime": 302.5952834645907,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
